==The beginning and history of Melo.==

[[At least 100 years ago]] the owner Sara Sioux created Melodramatic for the lulz. She accomplished this well and attracted [[Emo]] from all over Los Angeles like a moth to the flame. Little did she know that the mass influx of [[Emo]] would eventually overload and [[pwn]] her server. Thus melo [[fail|died]] and everybody's shit got [[pwn|erased]].

Since Emo are the biggest subscriber of [[butthurt]] they all got pissy, packed up their shit, and headed to [[MySpace]].

==Too many smoke rings?==
Most of the features of the old "1.0" version are still exactly the same as the current "1.9" version; which is actually supposed to be "2.0" but due to the owner blowing too many smoke rings and her lack of PHP coding skills she [[fail|FAILS]] it.

Much like High School, the Internets have formed groups and cliques. “Melo” only has [[OVER 9000|9000]] users, most of which are [[emo]] [[faggot]] [[basement dwellers]] who are either too [[fat|ugly]], or too full of [[fail]] to be a quality myspacer. Thus “Melo” is more or less a group of loners that everyone else throws apple-cores and other trash at during lunch.

